snippet.title: [Hindi] BGIS 2026 THE GRIND | Week 3 | Day 3
snippet.description:
Week 3 of The Grind is underway, and the race is starting to take real shape. With multiple weeks of action behind them, teams now know exactly where they stand. Every decision, every rotation, and every fight matters more than ever as the competition intensifies.

Group A:
iQOO ORANGUTAN
K9 Esports
iQOOSOUL
Infinix TrueRippers
Nebula Esports
OnePlus Gods Reign
Higgboson Esports
Madkings
iQOO RECKONING ESPORTS
iQOO8BIT
Team AX
Victores Sumus
Hero Xtreme Godlike
RAPID CHAOS ESPORTS
Blitz Esports
Autobotz Esports

Group B:
GENESIS ESPORTS
The Vanguard
Rising Esports
TWOB
EVOX Esports
Zutsu Esports
Wyld Fangs
SINEWY ESPORTS
4TR Official
NoNx Esports
TEAM X ESPORTS
LASTADE ESPORTS
The Knight Mobs
KALINGA ESPORTS
iQOO Team Tamilas
Team H4K

Expect high-pressure gameplay, sharper strategies, and moments that can shift the leaderboard in an instant. Whether teams are pushing to stay on top or fighting their way back into contention, this is where consistency and composure are truly tested.
Tune in, support your favourite teams, and watch the next chapter of BGIS 2026 unfold live.

Registrations for Rising Star 2026 are now open: https://bit.ly/RisingStar2026
Follow us on Instagram: https://instagram.com/KraftonIndiaEsports

#BGIS2026 #TheGrind #BreakingBoundaries #KRAFTONINDIAESPORTS #KIE #BGMI

snippet.title: Vadh 2 - Official Trailer | Sanjay Mishra, Neena Gupta | Jaspal Singh Sandhu | Luv Films | 6th Feb
snippet.description:
An old prison guard- Shambhunath Mishra (Sanjay Mishra) and a jail inmate- Manju Singh (Neena Gupta) share a bond forged behind prison walls. 

When their ordinary lives are pulled into a moral conflict and truth refuses to surface, they stand at the centre of a choice that has consequences.

#Vadh2 #SanjayMishra #NeenaGupta

A Luv Films presentation, Vadh 2 is written and directed by Jaspal Singh Sandhu and produced by Luv Ranjan and Ankur Garg. The film is slated for a theatrical release on 6th February 2026.

Starring: Sanjay Mishra, Neena Gupta with Kumud Mishra, Amitt K. Singh, Akshay Dogra, Shilpa Shukla & Yogita Bihani
Written & Directed By: Jaspal Singh Sandhu
Produced By: Luv Ranjan & Ankur Garg

Tod laaunga main

In havaon ko, in ghataaon ko

Mod laaunga main

In havaon ko, in ghataaon ko

Mohabbat ho gayi hai tumse

Mujhe kyun sataate ho tum

Laut aaunga main

Duniya se tujhe chura loon

Thoda intezar kar lo

Jitna bekaraar hoon main

Khud ko bekaraar kar lo

Kaise aitbar kar loon

snippet.title: Minecraft Speedrunner VS 5 Hunters REVIVAL
snippet.description:
You voted for it. Time to take on 5 hunters. The hunters are back and better than ever. Will we AT LAST move on to 6 hunters?

Follow my socials:
‚ûΩ Twitter - @dream
‚ûΩ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
‚ûΩ Snapchat - @dream

BadBoyHalo: @thesaintsofgames 
George: @GeorgeNotFound 
Sapnap: @Sapnap 
Antfrost: @Antfrost 
awesamdude: @awesamdude 

Seed: 935327412
Version: 1.21.11

We decided to call this series Minecraft Manhunt. This video is a different rendition of it, where there is FIVE hunters. The 6th rendition of the 5 hunters series, the revival...

This is a new Minecraft but, 1.21.11 challenge that we have decided to try. I try to beat the game, while my friends George and Sapnap and BadBoyHalo and Antfrost  and Awesamdude try to prevent me from doing it. It's a race, and it's super intense and we had a lot of laughs. I love doing these challenges.

(Most) Music is from: @dreamproductionsXD 

#MinecraftManhunt

Lyrics:
Mera karma tu mera dharma tu 
tera sab kuch mai mera sab kuch tu
[har karam apna karenge
har karam apna karenge aye watan tere liye
dil diya hai jan bhi denge aye watan tere liye] (x2)

tu mera karma tu mera dharma tu mera abhimaan hai
aye watan mehbub mere tujhpe dil kurbaan hai
aye watan mehbub mere tujhpe dil kurban hai
hum jiyenge or marenge aye watan tere liye
dil diya hai jaan bhi denge aye watan tere liye
dil diya hai jaan bhi denge aye watan tere liye

hindu muslim sikh isayi hum watan hum naam hai
hindu muslim sikh isayi hum watan hum naam hai
jo kare inko juda mazhab nahi ilzam hai
hum jiyenge or marenge aye watan tere liye
dil diya hai jaan bhi denge aye watan tere liye

teri galiyo me chalakar nafrato ki goliya

snippet.title: Teri Mitti | Kesari | Akshay Kumar, Parineeti Chopra | Arko | B Praak | Manoj M | Lyrical | 4K Video
snippet.description:
üëâüèª SUBSCRIBE to Timeless Tunes -https://bit.ly/4arAxZd
Song - Teri Mitti
Singer - B Praak 
Music - Arko
Lyrics - Manoj Muntashir
Programmed & Arranged by Aditya Dev
String Section performed live by Prakash Verma & Team
Strings conducted by Aditya Dev
Strings Recorded by Pankaj Kaushik at Taaleem Studios
Mix & Master - Eric Pillai (Future Sound of Bombay)
Mix Assistant - Micheal
Music Supervisor - Azeem Dayani

Starring - Akshay Kumar & Parineeti Chopra 
Directed by Anurag Singh 
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Aruna Bhatia, Karan Johar, Apoorva Mehta, Sunir Kheterpal 
Co-Produced by Amar Butala 
Written by Girish Kohli & Anurag Singh

Lyrics:

Talwaaron Pe Sar Vaar Diye 
Angaaron Mein Jism Jalaya Hai..
Ab Jaa Ke Kahin Humne Sar Pe
Yeh Kesari Rang Sajaya Hai..!!!

Ae Meri Zameen, Afsos Nahin
Jo Tere Liye Sau Dard Sahe..
Mehfooz Rahe, Teri Aan Sadaa 
Chaahe Jaan Meri Yeh Rahe Na Rahe..

Haa Meri Zameen, Mehboob Meri
Meri Nas-Nas Mein Tera Ishq Bahe
Pheeka Na Pade Kabhi Rang Tera
Jismon Se Nikal Ke Khoon Kahe..

Teri Mitti Mein Mil Jaawaan
Gul Ban Ke Main Khil Jaawaan
Itni Si, Hai Dil Ki Aarzu‚Ä¶.!!!

Teri Nadiyon Mein Beh Jaawaan..
Tere Kheton Mein Lehraawaan.. 
Itni Si, Hai Dil Ki Aarzu‚Ä¶.!!!

Sarson Se Bhare, Khaliyan Mere
Jahan Jhoom Ke Bhangda Paa Na Saka..  
Aabad Rahe, Woh Gaon Mera
Jahan Laut Ke Wapas Jaa Na Saka..

O Watna Ve, Mere Watna Ve
Tera Mera Pyaar Nirala Tha
Qurbaan Hua, Teri Asmat Pe
Main Kitna Naseebon Wala Tha

Teri Mitti Mein Mil Jaawaan
Gul Ban Ke Main Khil Jaawaan
Itni Si, Hai Dil Ki Aarzu‚Ä¶.!!!

Teri Nadiyon Mein Beh Jaawaan..
Tere Kheton Mein Lehraawaan.. 
Itni Si, Hai Dil Ki Aarzu‚Ä¶.!!!

Verse 3

O Heer Meri, Tu Hasti Rahe,
Teri Aankh Ghadi Bhar Nam Na Ho
Main Marta Tha, Jis Mukhde Pe
Kabhi Uska Ujala Kam Na Ho..

O Maayi Meri, Kya Fikr Tujhe
Kyun Aankh Se Dariya Behta Hai.. 
Tu Kehti Thi, Tera Chaand Hoon Main
Aur Chaand Humesha Rehta Hai..

Teri Mitti Mein Mil Jaawaan
Gul Ban Ke Main Khil Jaawaan
Itni Si, Hai Dil Ki Aarzu‚Ä¶.!!!

Teri Nadiyon Mein Beh Jaawaan..
Tere Faslon Mein Lehraawaan.. 
Itni Si, Hai Dil Ki Aarzu‚Ä¶.!!!


#KesariSongs #AkshayKumar #patrioticsongs

Kanda Sashti Kavasam is a powerful and sacred Tamil devotional hymn dedicated to Lord Murugan (Kartikeya). Listening or chanting Kanda Sashti Kavasam with deep devotion is believed to provide divine protection, courage, victory over enemies, good health, and spiritual strength. These Powerful Lord Murugan Tamil Bhakti Songs are ideal for daily prayers, Kanda Sashti days, meditation, and seeking Murugan‚Äôs blessings for peace and prosperity.

snippet.description:
"Diwana Hai Ye Man" from the film Chori Chori Chupke Chupke is a melodious romantic track sung by Sonu Nigam and Alka Yagnik, with music composed by Anu Malik. Featuring Salman Khan and Rani Mukerji, the song captures the fluttering emotions of love, innocence, and heartfelt longing. With its soothing melody, expressive vocals, and early-2000s Bollywood charm, this track remains a memorable and evergreen romantic favorite.
